divs: sighting detailshi, ive never done this and not sure your the people but at about 8:30pm california time. i was walking home when i seen 5-7red lights in a semi circle fly over me it remained a semi circle with dim white\grey area in the middle threw the cloud cover.each object having only 1 red light flashing not in unison heading in a southern direction from hanford, california. i thought at 1rst maybe it was from the local naval air base but why so many lights and no sound? and this isnt the 1st time ive seen things over my home.
